{"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-aaa573aabb44ca52d7a3795e5528b01a_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "69 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2050957003342733424"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIwNitzumWj8tEEAMaCTEyMDAzNzE1MiDusM7RBjAAOCBAE3ITMjA1MDk1NzAwMzM0MjczMzQyNHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1781926881.894050", "card_id": "Q_350075934", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1093}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "哪部动漫的某个片段让你至今难忘？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-84c294421db62a8f54cba782ac217b9c_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "67 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/350075934"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IwNitzumWj8tEEAMaCDQwMDcyNjk3IOqA/ewFMAA4mipAFHIJMzUwMDc1OTM0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1781926881.894310", "card_id": "Q_2050584252303893056", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 26}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "导演於水直言 AI 是无所不能的大模型，每个人是不完美的小模型，不完美才能产生艺术，你认可这种说法吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "上海国际电影节 上海国际电影节金爵论坛上《浪浪山小妖怪》导演於水谈是否担心 AI 模仿融合自己的动画风格。 於水：这是科学问题也是一个哲学问题，可能会有这么一天，所以它无所不能。AI 是基于大模型，我在想我们每个人相当于一个「小模型」。小模型的意思是它不完美不完备，大模型无所不知，世界的一切，古往今来所有的历史知识，所有的推演方法科研方法它都知道，人有局限性的。 但是正是因为我们是小模型，不完美才会构成了人类的喜怒哀乐。大模型没有喜怒哀乐，没有欲求，没有诉求，就没有艺术。艺术本质上就是人类痛苦喜悦所诞生的东西。 所以从哲学角度来说，我觉得可能还是只有我们不完美才能产生艺术。大模型它可能产生不了，如果它能产生也只是模拟，也是概率的一种模拟而已，它不是真切的人类的情感。 作为人类我们是某一个艺术的接收方，我们需要有一种共鸣，创作者也得理解我们，我们是相通的，而不是大模型一个高高在上，居高临下，模拟的事情让你来理解，我们来共鸣，我们可能还做不到。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-e0f3fff1d7a0c23c9aa919d160e0ab58_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "65 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2050584252303893056"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIwNitzumWj8tEEAMaCTEyMDAyMTAwNiDH+sjRBjAAOCBAFXITMjA1MDU4NDI1MjMwMzg5MzA1NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1781926881.895179", "card_id": "Q_2045842898327795610", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "AI 最容易在哪些内容上说得头头是道，却不一定靠谱？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "技术越是强大，那些「并不高效但属于我」的痕迹，就越珍贵。 你无需证明，只需记录，我们邀请你一起共建一场充满「人味」的讨论场。让过去的创造、今天的尝试，还有未来的每一步——都带着人类的温度，被看见、被留下… 2026 人文季正式启动｜活动主会场 ⬇️知乎 2026 人文季「本来就很棒的人类」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-a09eaca4a2a1ac3182a339dfc0bf2da6_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "61 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2045842898327795610"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIwNitzumWj8tEEAMaCTExOTgwOTA1MSCM+4PRBjAAOB9AFnITMjA0NTg0Mjg5ODMyNzc5NTYxMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1781926881.895684", "card_id": "Q_2046245615697409853", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 25}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "文科生学习编程有必要吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": 